Missions.Title: The hideout I
Missions.Description: You enter the cave, as the smugglers open fire. Joke is on them, since you are armed to the teeth.

Missions.Title: The hideout II
Missions.Description: You start collecting clues as some paramilitary units enter the cave and start attacking.

Missions.Title: Way to the base
Missions.Description: As you leave the cave, you check the terrain for snipers.  It's more a habit, but you actually find some. Get the hell out of the area!

Missions.Title: Dept. for Information Security
Missions.Description: The files contain information about a weapon trade. A lot of high-tech explosives have been bought for a lot of money. The papers also include security codes for the buyers computer. You know an IT expert that could help, but you better hurry, because the opponent party is after her.

Objectives.Description: Find the IT expert before the enemy does

Missions.Title: Sergeant Fourquad
Missions.Description: It turns out, a guy Sergeant Fourquad is planning something terrible. He plans to blow up the next Ogre Space Station to start a war and to stay employed. You decide to end this madness and ask the IT expert to switch off the intruder alert.

Objectives.Description: Rid some guards to get into the building.

Missions.Title: Inside the mansion
Missions.Description: The IT expert manages to switch off the security systems. Now it's your turn to blow up the explosives and take out the sergeant.
